{jjdpr_pace}
key must match `₣[A-Za-z0-9_-]{5}` and start with parent
{jjdhr_heat}
key
. Each
{jjdpr_pace}
must have:
{jjdpm_silks}
(non-empty kebab-case),
`tacks` (non-empty array)
. Each
{jjdkr_tack}
must have:
{jjdkm_refined}
(YYMMDD-HHMM),
{jjdkm_state}
({jjdpe_pending},
{jjdpe_current},
{jjdpe_complete},
